---
description: Lean comments on non-obvious logic only
globs: "**/*.{ts,tsx,sql}"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Complex Code Comments

Add **lean comments** only where a human (or agent) would struggle without context:

- RLS policies and security rules (SQL)
- Realtime subscription lifecycle (subscribe/unsubscribe, channel naming)
- Auth flows (magic-link callback, session exchange)
- Permission checks that encode product rules

Do **not** comment self-explanatory UI, simple getters, or obvious Chakra layout.
